page.title: 01Review of Much Wenlock area.
page.content: This{4km. by 3km. block}includes the majority of the town of{Much Wenlock, and the{countryside to the south of {this town. The town of{Much Wenlock}is a{small {country town}with a{population}of {2,486.}The majority of people living in Much Wenlock travel to other towns to work and therefore{employment in {this town is very limited.}However, although{Much Wenlock}is a small town, it has a{Primary School, three {Churches, several interesting historic {buildings}and{many organizations and {clubs}providing leisure time activities. {The countryside}to the south of Much Wenlock is all{farming land,}where the majority of fields contain{crops}or {cultivated grass.
